<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a24Mar1924"><font color="red">24 March 1924</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): In making notes I used signs for the various characters. It may amuse you to see them so I shall write them on the back of this. &hellip; Shaun is going to give me a very great deal of trouble. &hellip; <b><font face="wake">H</font></b> (Earwicker, H C E by moving letter round)  <b><font face="wake">A</font></b> Anna Livia <b><font face="wake">C</font></b> Shem-Cain <b><font face="wake">D</font></b> Shaun  <b><font face="wake">W</font></b> Snake <b><font face="wake">P</font></b> S. Patrick <b><font face="wake">T</font></b> Tristan  <b><font face="wake">I</font></b> Isolde  <b><font face="wake">X</font></b> Mamalujo <b><font face="wake">N</font></b> This stands for the title but I do not wish to say it yet until the book has written more of itself. </div>
